{"title":"汉俳四章","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉俳四章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谒秋瑾墓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亭边碧血凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿姓字关兴亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古颂秋娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上几沧桑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅里西湖碧汪汪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人犹话镠王。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：镠王，指五代时吴越国的建立者钱镠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登六和塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处起高楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六和塔望大江流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形胜说从头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今说钟情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁解钟情到死生？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独对断桥亭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９０年春，学写于在杭州召开的“歌俳诗国际研讨会”期间。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}